            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Mettius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Volt</abbr><ex>inia</ex></expan> Valens <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXVIII <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XIIX <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes aedicula mit der Büste eines Mannes; im Giebel weibliche Büste; unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes Darstellung einer Tür. Datierung: nachdem die legio VII den Beinamen &amp;quot;&amp;quot;C(laudia) p(ia) f(idelis)&amp;quot;&amp;quot; erhalten hatte (42 n. Chr.) und bevor sie Dalmatien verließ (um 56/57 n. Chr.).</p>
            </div>
